{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 52,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الطُّورِ",
    "englishName": "At-Tur",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Mount",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 49,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4736,
        "text": "以山发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4737,
        "text": "—",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4738,
        "text": "以记录在展开的羊皮纸上的经典[《古兰经》]发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4739,
        "text": "以人类朝觐的天房发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4740,
        "text": "以高耸的天穹发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4741,
        "text": "以汪洋大海发誓[或以复活日被点烧的大海发誓]！",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4742,
        "text": "你的主的刑罚肯定是要来临的，",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4743,
        "text": "任何人都不能抵抗它。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4744,
        "text": "当天体[恐怖地]震动之日，",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4745,
        "text": "群山将被移毁。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4746,
        "text": "在那日，否认真理者将遭严惩真活该！",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4747,
        "text": "因为他们在妄谈中取乐。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4748,
        "text": "当他们被强行推入火狱之日，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4749,
        "text": "[有话声对他们说]：“这就是你们[生前]所否认的火狱。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4750,
        "text": "这是魔术呢？还是你们看不见？",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4751,
        "text": "你们尝试火刑吧！无论你们能忍受，还是不能忍受，对你们都是一样的。你们只受你们所犯罪恶的还报。”",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4752,
        "text": "敬畏者必在乐园和恩泽中，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4753,
        "text": "[他们]欣喜于他们的主赐予他们的[恩惠]。他们的主已拯救他们脱离火狱的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4754,
        "text": "[有话声对他们说]：“你们因你们所做的善功愉快地吃喝吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4755,
        "text": "[他们]靠在成排的宝椅上，我将白净美目贤淑的美女做他们的妻子。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4756,
        "text": "凡自己信仰，其子孙也同他们一起信仰者，我将使他们的子孙[在乐园里]与他们团聚[注1]，我不会减少他们的任何善功[注2]。每人都应对自己所做的事负责。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4757,
        "text": "我将把他们想要的水果和肉食赐给他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4758,
        "text": "他们将在乐园里互相传递酒杯[敬酒]，[他们]不会因此[饮酒]口出秽言，也不会因此[饮酒]而犯罪[在乐园里饮酒是合法的]。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4759,
        "text": "他们的[男]童仆在旁边服侍他们，那些童仆犹如蚌壳里的珍珠。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4760,
        "text": "他们彼此走来，互相询问。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4761,
        "text": "他们说：“以前，我们的确为我们的家人畏惧[安拉的刑罚]，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4762,
        "text": "但[现在]安拉已施恩给我们，并拯救我们脱离了火狱的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4763,
        "text": "以前，我们的确常祈求他。他确是仁爱的，特慈的。”",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4764,
        "text": "你[穆圣]当[以伊斯兰教]教诲[人类]。凭你的主的恩惠，你既不是占卜者，也不是疯子。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4765,
        "text": "或许他们要说：“[他]是个诗人，我们等待他[穆圣]遭不幸。”",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4766,
        "text": "你[对他们]说：“你们等待吧！我的确也同你们一起等待。”",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4767,
        "text": "是他们的理智教他们如此妄言呢？还是他们是叛逆的民众？",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4768,
        "text": "难道他们要说：“他[穆圣]伪造它[《古兰经》]？”不，是他们不信仰。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4769,
        "text": "假如他们是诚实者，叫他们作出[与《古兰经》]同样的经文来！",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4770,
        "text": "是他们从无到有被创造呢？还是他们就是创造者？",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4771,
        "text": "难道他们创造了天地吗？不，是他们不笃信[安拉]。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4772,
        "text": "是他们拥有你的主的宝藏呢？还是他们有权为所欲为？",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4773,
        "text": "难道他们有一把梯子能[登天]窃听[天使们的谈话]吗？[要是这样]，让他们的窃听者拿出明证来吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4774,
        "text": "难道女孩归他[安拉]而男孩归你们吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4775,
        "text": "难道你[穆圣]向他们索取过[传教的]报酬，因而他们为纳税负担太重吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4776,
        "text": "难道他们知道未见之物，因而他们能把它记录下来吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4777,
        "text": "难道他们想阴谋迫害[你]吗？不信仰者必自中其计。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4778,
        "text": "除安拉外，难道他们还有应受崇拜的主吗？赞美安拉超绝！他超绝于他们所崇拜的[偶像]。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4779,
        "text": "假如他们能看见一块天掉下来，他们必说：“[这只是]一片浓云。”",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4780,
        "text": "你别理他们！直到他们遭遇他们被震晕的日子。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4781,
        "text": "在那日，他们的计谋对他们将毫无益处，他们也得不到任何援助。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4782,
        "text": "此前，不义者还要受另一种刑罚[注][在尘世所遭受的灾难和坟墓中审问时的刑罚]，但他们大多数人并不知道。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4783,
        "text": "你[穆圣]当耐心等待你的主的判决，因为你确是在我的眷顾之下的。你起床时应赞美颂扬你的主；",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4784,
        "text": "在夜间和星辰没落时，你也应赞颂他。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "zh.mazhonggang",
